## Template placeholders - replace the ${...} tokens with real values or create a
## runtime env.properties that defines these variables.

## Gateway-internal JWT signing secret (must match ProductService).
## Used by Gateway to sign short-lived JWTs for internal /internal/** routes.
## Recommended length: >= 32 bytes (HS256).
GATEWAY_INTERNAL_JWT_SECRET=${GATEWAY_INTERNAL_JWT_SECRET}
